# Review Platform rules

- New work belongs under `apps/review-platform/`. Do not modify legacy ExtJS/Roo under `src/` unless explicitly asked.
- Backend API prefix is `/api/v1`.
- Load the matching project skill before large changes: `spring-boot-java25`, `angular-review-ui`, `drools-assignment-rules`, or `cprs-domain-model`.
- Keep Drools facts separate from JPA entities.
- Prefer Flyway migrations over `ddl-auto=update` for shared schemas.
